WEBVTT

00:12:56.240 --> 00:13:00.136
and shape into some perfect
form of a human

00:13:00.160 --> 00:13:03.656
that might just be perfect enough
to warrant them admission

00:13:03.680 --> 00:13:06.120
to one of the most
highly selective colleges.

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:10.920
But I've come to realize, after working
with thousands of other people's kids --

00:13:11.640 --> 00:13:13.360
(Laughter)

00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:16.800
and raising two kids of my own,

00:13:18.200 --> 00:13:20.400
my kids aren't bonsai trees.

00:13:21.800 --> 00:13:23.520
They're wildflowers

00:13:24.400 --> 00:13:27.216
of an unknown genus and species --

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:29.136
(Laughter)

00:13:29.160 --> 00:13:32.576
and it's my job to provide
a nourishing environment,